OL,3,CAlmost 100 mile detour as major
OL,4,Croadworks start on the A75 tonight
OL,6,FThe second phase of major roadworks on
OL,7,Fthe A75 are due to start tonight.
OL,9,FThe road will be closed between
OL,10,FAuchenlarie and Mossyard from 8pm to
OL,11,F6am.
OL,13,FDrivers will face a 96 mile detour via
OL,14,FGirvan and Ayr, causing delays of up
OL,15,Fto two-and-a-half hours.
