OL,6,FJohn Carruthers' haulage company uses
OL,7,Fthe road regularly and said: "If
OL,8,Fthey'd put a convoy system into place
OL,9,Fso that the road was still open for
OL,10,Fsomebody, built it up into a duel
OL,11,Fcarriageway when it was supposed to,
OL,12,Fthen that would've made a big
OL,13,Fdifference.
OL,15,F"They wouldn't have needed to shut the
OL,16,Froad at all, but it's something that
OL,17,Fnever happened."
