OL,6,FThe company behind the works, Amey,
OL,7,Fsay they have taken every step to
OL,8,Freduce disruption, including working
OL,9,Fat night.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Amey, said: "The
OL,12,Fcarriageway of the A75 at Auchenlarie
OL,13,Fand Mossyard is reaching the end of
OL,14,Fits operational life and is in need of
OL,15,Frepair.
OL,17,F"Doing this work now, will prevent
OL,18,Fthese roads deteriorating during the
OL,19,Fwinter period, which would cause more
OL,20,Fextensive disruption and inconvenience.
