OL,6,F"The dates of the work were arrived
OL,7,Fat, in consultation with residents and
OL,8,Fbusinesses on this route, and special
OL,9,Faccess arrangements have been made for
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"As well as local engagement there has
OL,13,Fbeen extensive discussion with ferry
OL,14,Foperators, the haulage industry, and
OL,15,Fthe emergency services to mitigate the
OL,16,Fimpact of this scheme.
OL,18,F"By working overnight, and off-peak,
OL,19,Fevery attempt has been made to reduce
OL,20,Fdisruption."
